Originally ripped by Terminal Escape, posted on November 07, 2023 Description from Terminal Escape:
The most gloriously snotty raw punk I've come across in ages; ramshackle lo-fi hardcore manifested in a basement in Argentina. Five songs here...and all you're going to want is five more. You can't have them, so you'll listen again.DEGOLLADA
